/www.ian-leslie.com/p/how-silicon-valley-hacked-the-science">硅谷如何黑客行为</a><strong><br></strong><a href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/the-tortoise">凯尔·斯塔默，乌龟</a></em></p></blockquote><p>为专家们考虑一下。任何以评论英国政治为生的人在过去几年一定过得很艰难。叙事发展明显缺乏。保守党政府已经无可挽回地崩溃了，工党有望赢得下一次选举，但并没有激发太多热情。实在是能说的就这么多了，而且已经说死了。媒体勇敢地试图从这种停滞状态中挤出一些戏剧性的东西，但本质上它是<em>等待戈多，</em>没有幽默感或神秘感。</p><p>里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）的表现低于本已很低的预期，为整个时期带来了一个惊喜。他打出了一手糟糕透顶的牌。他现在是唯一剩下的有趣的问题了；问题是，为什么他的工作表现如此糟糕？为什么他在这方面的表现比几乎所有政治观察家预测的还要差？他是如何从党内最伟大的人才变成一位增加了保守党在下次选举中被彻底终结的可能性的领导人？</p><p>我们需要谈谈 Rishi，但首先，让我们提醒自己事情是如何发生的，同时向那些可能没有关注这个国家令人作呕的政治喜剧的人补充一下。</p><p><a href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/the-sunak-question">阅读更多</a></p>; 
Why Does Being Left-Wing Make You Unhappy?The Ideological Well-Being Gap https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/why-does-being-left-wing-make-you https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/why-does-being-left-wing-make-youIan Leslie Sat, 13 Apr 2024 09:02:58 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4473ce8a-8a15-4ebd-b9d5-eba0670c7f26_1600x1200.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4473ce8a-8a15-4ebd-b9d5-eba0670c7f26_1600x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4473ce8a-8a15-4ebd-b9d5-eba0670c7f26_1600x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4473ce8a-8a15-4ebd-b9d5-eba0670c7f26_1600x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4473ce8a-8a15-4ebd-b9d5-eba0670c7f26_1600x1200.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4473ce8a-8a15-4ebd-b9d5-eba0670c7f26_1600x1200.jpeg" width="656" height="492" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4473ce8a-8a15-4ebd-b9d5-eba0670c7f26_1600x1200.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscree