模仿天才吗？</a><strong><br></strong><a href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/why-londons-famous-penguin-pool-has">伦敦空荡荡的企鹅池</a><strong><br></strong><a href="https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/am-i-anti-woke">我是反觉醒者吗？</a></em></p></blockquote><p><br><em>注意：这个版本对于电子邮件来说显然有点太长了，所以您可能想通过单击上面的标题（或底部的链接）在线阅读。</em><br><br>在过去十二年左右的时间里，年轻人的心理健康状况明显恶化，目前引起了人们的广泛关注。争论的焦点集中在技术上。然而，即使<a href="https://twitter.com/JonHaidt/status/1437836289332629505">手机</a>是罪魁祸首，它们也可能不是唯一的原因。值得注意的是，“社会正义”话语（有时被称为<a href="https://www.vox.com/2019/3/22/18259865/great-awokening-white-liberals-race-polling-trump-2020">“大觉醒”</a> ）的日益突出也发生在同一时期。请原谅我的粗略代理： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142eb14e-7f94-41b7-8ab8-fea9b907077e_2512x922.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142eb14e-7f94-41b7-8ab8-fea9b907077e_2512x922.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142eb14e-7f94-41b7-8ab8-fea9b907077e_2512x922.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142eb14e-7f94-41b7-8ab8-fea9b907077e_2512x922.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142eb14e-7f94-41b7-8ab8-fea9b907077e_2512x922.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:ste